text: Superb kopi and great eggs & kaya toast. Kopi is always consistently great! Friendly uncle and aunties prepping the food and drinks.

Had kopi tit loh ($1.10) after my breakfast, was good & affordable! Relatively strong and aromatic. I'll be back to have my coffee fix here.
Their yuan yang(coffee with tea, $1.30) is big cup, smooth, slightly thick, less sweet and has some coffee/tea aroma. 9/10

Best kopi and teh in marine terrace food centre. Nice and thick. The best coffee out of the 3 kopi stalls. Takeaway coffee to work everyday.

Fast queues. Usually they are closed on Wednesdays.
